Si’ool akka qileetti mul’ateera (Luuqaas 8:31; Mul’ata 9:1) akkasuma galaana  ibiddaa, dhagaa boba’u, bakka warri keessa jiraatan halkaniif guyyaa bara hanga bara baraatti itti dhiphatan(Mul’ata 20:10).
