Jireenyi biyya lafaa irraa qorannaadha, waanta dhufaa jiruuf qophaa’uu.
Amantootaaaf, jireenyi du’a boodaa jireenya bara baraati mootummaa waaqaa keessa Waaqayyoo wajjin.
